data.value:
In this project we are focusing on developing a 2D racing car game.
This project will cover the implementation of little graphics, physics engine, sound effects and background music.
Our idea is about to create an adventure and action based video game whose main purpose is to provide really entertaining experience to the people of age group between 8 to 15. For achieving this goal, we have used the Visual Basic and MySql Database.
Our game consists of Levels ,where increase in levels there will be increase in hardness, and this game will make the player to make his mind Active.
